      "body_md": "## AuditToolkit Suite 2026.1 — RC1\n\nCore audit orchestration server and all three remote agent packages.\n\n**Install (Debian/Ubuntu):**\n`dpkg -i audit-tool_1.0.0~rc1_amd64.deb`\n\n**Agents:**\n- `fleet-agent` — managed poll/callback agent; requires AUDIT_SERVER_URL in /etc/audittoolkit/fleet-agent/agent.env\n- `standalone-agent` — local web UI agent (port 8088)\n- `cmdb-agent` — CMDB discovery agent (port 9001); requires AGENT_API_KEY\n\n**SHA-256 checksums:**\n```\nf57edbc59cef1c572b0693bd1d519f40f15b53ed75cad038fd71641b58df905f  audit-tool_1.0.0~rc1_amd64.deb\nba3269c9c2c55030a1ee26a8f642fca3ea7b1557c35d8193422544d7ddacfcd8  fleet-agent_1.0.0~rc1_amd64.deb\n31428e7b9eee66c28800a575302d22f254a7ce83aa890cc18f21d6870954bacb  standalone-agent_1.0.0~rc1_amd64.deb\nbacb8d8a8791e248b5df3a795ab42067ac6d1e2e513db00dff53acb5db18eb6a  cmdb-agent_1.0.0~rc1_amd64.deb\n18d1b9ea51178aa9ebbd61ebfc31990d5536ca59e9cdf820604c0ca14ec7e321  fleet-agent-1.0.0-0.rc1.x86_64.rpm\n6b348dc4f2a1c2f22578561fcb2e3639349f601559442be88570fccd77d69179  standalone-agent-1.0.0-0.rc1.x86_64.rpm\ne026ecc0cf2fa94f7bd15421a6514542cb540a13928f3790bce4981c8e28a386  cmdb-agent-1.0.0-0.rc1.x86_64.rpm\n```",
